      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "お、ちょうど良かった\n{user}君を探してたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ just in time.\n{user}‚ I've been looking for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、相談に乗ってもらえないかな？\n……出来れば、他のみんながいない所で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ can you help me with a consultation?\n…… if you can‚ where everyone else isn't.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……？　あぁ、分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……?　Yeah‚ I got it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "良かった。それじゃ、行こうか。……ついでに\nランチも出来ると嬉しいね。お腹空いちゃったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good. Let's go then. I'd be happy\nto eat lunch too. I'm starving.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に相談なんだろうな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it really a consultation……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.666666600002,
          "startTime": 29.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 28.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "それで\n{user}君に相談というのはね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚\nI need to tell you‚ {user} ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 34
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなの好みを教えてもらおうと思って\n好きなものとか、食べられないものとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was wondering if you could tell me what everyone at Hoshimi Pro likes.\nWhat they like or what they can't eat ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "食べ物だけじゃなくていいんだ。趣味とか特技\n可愛いのとカッコいいのどっちが好きかとかでも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't have to be just about food. Or hobbies‚ or skills‚\nor whether they like ‚ cute or cool‚ anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいけど……どうして急にそんなことを？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ but …… why are you suddenly asking that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "この間、バレンタインのチョコを\nみんなに作ると言ったよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day I said I'm\ngoing to make Valentine's Day chocolates for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 57.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "どうせならみんなが気に入ってくれるものにしたいしね\nそのリサーチという訳だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I want to make sure everyone likes it anyway.\nThat's why I need to do a research.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 64.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなって、リズノワだけじゃなくて全員なのか！？\nそれもみんな別々にだなんて、大変だろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By everyone‚ do you mean everyone‚ not just LizNoir!?\nIt must be hard to do that all separately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "心配しなくても、そんなに大したことはしないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry‚ it won't be that big a deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 76.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "パティスリーじゃないんだから\n出来ることだって限られてるしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not a patisserie‚\nso what I can do is limited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "形やアイシング、デコレーションを変えるとか\n後は、ラッピングを変えるくらいかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can only change the shape‚ icing‚ decorations‚\nand maybe the wrapping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと個性をつけるだけで\n一個一個の印象もぐっと変わると思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think just a little bit of individuality\ncan make each piece look a lot different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あいしん……なんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aishin …… what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "アイシングね。ドーナツとかでよくあるやつだよ\n溶いた砂糖でデコレーションされてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Icing. You know‚ the kind you see on doughnuts and stuff.\nThey're decorated with melted sugar.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 106.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ！　あれか、砂糖がチョコがけみたいになってる\nお菓子作りが得意と聞いてたけど、そこまでとは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! I see. It's like sugar on chocolate.\nI heard you were good at baking‚ but I didn't realize you were that good. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "言ったじゃないか、莉央には毎年作ってたって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you‚ I made it for Rio every year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、最近の僕はもらってばかりだったから\n食べる方のイメージが強かったかもしれないけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Well‚ maybe because I'm always the one who receive‚\nso I've always had a strong image of the eater‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから、出来るところを見せたいじゃないか\nだからほら、みんなの好みを教えてよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that I want to show people I do cook.\nSo come on‚ tell me what those guys like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 134.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ\nそういうことなら、俺も協力しない訳にはいかないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.\nIf that's the case‚ I'm sure in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
